{"tid":971737,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「不嫁我就殺妳」變態男示愛 女醫師崩潰","createTime":"2019-01-07T01:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T02:21:33.000Z","uid":32511,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"589ecb5dd463be65fdd03fe57c6804f7db49e0fb","tid":971737,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T01:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6tQJL9Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6tQJL9Q.png&h=0ddb9021&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名女醫師保養得宜，年逾40，看不出歲月痕跡。沒想到因工作關係，結識張姓男業務（40歲），竟演變成噩夢一場。<br />\n <br />\n張男初見女醫師驚為天人，展開猛烈追求，但女醫師不來電，予以婉拒。<br />\n <br />\n某日凌晨2點，張男開車至女醫師住處堵人，女醫師見狀跑開，張男卻持鋁棒追上，女醫師擔心遭遇不測，無奈帶張男進屋聊天。<br />\n <br />\n《自由時報》報導，張男除了傾訴愛慕之情，甚至不准女醫師打瞌睡、上廁所，還說「2個月內不嫁給我就幹掉妳！」<br />\n <br />\n女醫師假意順從，張男才離去，過程長達4小時。天亮後女醫師提告，警方將張男依恐嚇等罪嫌送辦。"},{"pid":"067d0f517a2677dcf0d7a4c81f108018b843bb72","tid":971737,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T01:02:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afffbd617392f7ac244a55b8d787172c213095a3","tid":971737,"uid":3698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T01:03:36.000Z","msg":"原始人<br />\n一棍落去帶返屋企"},{"pid":"efcd31ea5e555fc2d961ec5ade5d77f4b8e846b0","tid":971737,"uid":20337,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"afffbd617392f7ac244a55b8d787172c213095a3","tid":971737,"uid":3698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T01:03:36.000Z","msg":"原始人<br />\n一棍落去帶返屋企"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T01:42:35.000Z","msg":"殘忍只需一棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來謙謙句歌詞係咁深奧"},{"pid":"ad75d791005f959312fb428d953feac1f8f5a9ec","tid":971737,"uid":128223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T02:07:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce1c0f181e5394fff3e44298723972b86b67d11b","tid":971737,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T02:15:37.000Z","msg":"呢個男嘅咁忍